{"tid":1483690,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張建宗籲回歸理性停止暴力","createTime":"2019-08-18T12:47:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T14:37:08.000Z","uid":14921,"like":64,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"5acb96ccdabb2b44ddbd5c9376ae82e08ff27d9f","tid":1483690,"uid":14921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T12:47:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">政務司司長張建宗表示，要先回歸理性，停止暴力，香港才能重新出發。</span> <br />\n<br />\n張建宗發表網誌，指超過兩個月的示威遊行，演變成的不合作運動和暴力行為，嚴重影響市民生活和社會秩序，法治和道德底線受到衝擊，重創香港國際形象。他認為真正愛護和關心香港的人，是絕不會犧牲社會的安寧，更不會破壞多年來苦心經營的社會民生建設，所以暴力行為必須停止，各方面要放下成見和仇恨，確保一國兩制繼續成功實踐，才有機會回歸理性，讓香港復元和重新出發。<br />\n<br />\n今日回歸咗和平啦<br />\n重新出發啦俾你<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可</span></span>"},{"pid":"b7bc9336f5ea1b1a8d67d6c2e54c4622ac5c2329","tid":1483690,"uid":48427,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T12:49:04.000Z","msg":"和平左啦 政府出發未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"244eb0650a32a8a609c935ed6c1300395f7d8211","tid":1483690,"uid":25183,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T12:49:45.000Z","msg":"今日好和平喎"},{"pid":"ff126c9fe92dd6a0b5cd8aa536b8fd9c243fad9d","tid":1483690,"uid":156579,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T12:52:16.000Z","msg":"睇你做撚到啲乜 乜都做唔到又可以升級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec118e06acfdf9b699637eed22dab4c954df822a","tid":1483690,"uid":152222,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T12:52:42.000Z","msg":"果然係錄音機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab97a31860848ec1bd4f5275ae5ab1f1f24ef2e6","tid":1483690,"uid":75745,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T12:53:14.000Z","msg":"所以無跟劇本<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b5d1c787d025b5cad90c7a760eb9c2f60668739","tid":1483690,"uid":14494,"li